{"tid":1351324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住係我錯","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T15:26:26.000Z","uid":98465,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0556f5bf66a81b8f6f3ddad70122de9a284cb704","tid":1351324,"uid":98465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"同我推撚返晒上去<br />\n元朗上環一嚟發生，一齊推<br />\n<br />\n<strong>上環Video 整合 (粗略) (keep updating) </strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1</a> <br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=5ea49662\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=6b8a7efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=b97a406b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=f5e472dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=bd524418\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=de4a46e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=9ecdb312\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=f8be4009\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=a10a9f98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=bf77a818\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=65696e34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n\t<br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=2586bb18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=5b33ccc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t<br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。 <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=cffa9ae8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭 <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2%2F%2FZYLwdG